ActNunavut Act
SubjectNunavut Court of Justice - Deputy Judges (a) Hon. Rosemary E. Nation (b) Hon. Bonnie R. Warkentin (c) Hon. Maureen P. Forestell (d) Hon. Casimir N. Herold
PrecisOrder appointing the Honourables (a) Rosemary E. Nation, (b) Bonnie R. Warkentin, (c) Maureen P. Forestell, and (d) Casimir N. Herold as Deputy Judges of the Nunavut Court of Justice to hold office during good behaviour until attaining the age of seventy-five years.
